As Dr. Will Caster works toward his goal of creating an omniscient, sentient machine, a radical anti-technology organization fights to prevent him from establishing a world where computers can transcend the abilities of the human brain.

Director: Wally Pfister
Writer: Jack Paglen
Stars: Johnny Depp, Rebecca Hall, Morgan Freeman
Genres: Drama | Mystery | Sci-Fi | Thriller
Country: UK | China | USA
Language: English


SOURCE: R6 CAM

RLS NOTES: First CAM, don't expect amazing quality. Took the source file and
first of all had to cut off the first 30 secs or so of video due to a horrible
site watermark, could have left it on but the audio and video was a mess anyway.
Then made sure the hardcoded subtitles were fully cropped off the bottom of the
video. Cropped, Resized, Brightness/Contrast, HSV, RGB, Sharpen/Smoother and then 
converted to XviD, had a little mess with the audio and then converted and muxed it 
back over the video. Check the sample first and then either take it or leave it... 
Your choice folks :)
